{"tid":2237584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"看中國臉色行事？ 南韓政府被爆隱瞞中國軍機入侵次數","createTime":"2020-10-10T11:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T12:06:48.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b29aecbac14b63d270c26411c4eb501af4005ae4","tid":2237584,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"南韓《中央日報》報導，軍方刻意隱瞞了文在寅政府時期，中國軍機入侵南韓防空識別區（KADIZ）的次數，指文在寅上台後，中國軍機無端入侵南韓防空識別區的次數增加，而政府卻只為了避免外交摩擦，而看中國的臉色行事。<br />\n<br />\n南韓聯合參謀本部提交的2016-2019年中俄軍機進入南韓防空識別區的資料顯示，2016和2017年的相關記錄分別有50多次和70多次，2018年增加到140多次，去年再減至50多次。<br />\n<br />\n但與該部門去年12月的內部資料不符。這份報告顯示，2016和2017年入侵次數分別為40多次和60多次，少於向國會提交的資料，而2018年次數則高達200多次，比公開資料多出60多次，去年資料更是比公開資料多100多次，達150多次，是公開資料的三倍。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，震驚不少人，有前軍方高層相關人士說，統計可能有出入，但不可能差這麼多，懷疑可能有人對資料動手腳。 還有匿名的軍方人士表示，從2018年開始瞞報入侵次數，可能與文在寅的外交政策有關，能夠看出政府在看中國的臉色，並指一心推動中國國家主席習近平訪韓的文在寅政府，可能擔心國內反中輿論高漲，因而故意隱瞞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201010/44MGMT4ZOJCLVGZ57ZQGAGBJCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201010%2F44MGMT4ZOJCLVGZ57ZQGAGBJCY%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=d189d338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201010%2F44MGMT4ZOJCLVGZ57ZQGAGBJCY%2F&h=df59b3da\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201010/44MGMT4ZOJCLVGZ57ZQGAGBJCY/</a>"},{"pid":"40a9f43200abe05b7dbdf7db760235439f16e3ef","tid":2237584,"uid":59511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"Britain and France had to choose between war and dishonour. They chose dishonour. They will have war."},{"pid":"99e0853bb7d628dced70c8e5a5a58d7bd7e75149","tid":2237584,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d77af63f175bd6737f5d5bacf7589c2064f0937","tid":2237584,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"南韓國民其實係點評價佢地個總統？定係無所謂是但搵個做就ok?"},{"pid":"882555c38ec1a22475f2948196513ab7efe61073","tid":2237584,"uid":232077,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0d77af63f175bd6737f5d5bacf7589c2064f0937","tid":2237584,"uid":2110,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"南韓國民其實係點評價佢地個總統？定係無所謂是但搵個做就ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cmmedia.com.tw/file/14124/1521002688_3_20180314-%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E5%A0%B4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmmedia.com.tw%2Ffile%2F14124%2F1521002688_3_20180314-%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4.jpg&h=34e86254&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}